<p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(71, 71, 71); letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; background-color: rgb(255, 249, 240);"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240509/1715241803822085292.png" title="1715241803822085292.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-09 155832.png" width="690" height="520" style="width: 690px; height: 520px;"/></span></p><p style="text-align: left; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(71, 71, 71); letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; background-color: rgb(255, 249, 240);"><br/></span></p><p style="text-align: left; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(71, 71, 71); letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px;">江西软件职业技术大学</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(71, 71, 71); letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; caret-color: red; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">为促进教师专业化水平、创新能力和信息化教学应用能力全面提升，于2024年 4 月 30 日开展了“第十四届青年教师教学竞赛决赛”，在此次竞赛中，经济管理学院赵鸣华老师《音乐鉴赏》课程荣获文科思政类的一等奖。</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(71, 71, 71); letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; caret-color: red; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240509/1715241919549077733.png" title="1715241919549077733.png" alt="微信图片_20240509155903.png" width="996" height="596" style="width: 996px; height: 596px;"/></span></p><p style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: red; color: rgb(33, 33, 34); letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">在赵鸣华老师的课程上，同学们都踊跃参与，积极思考，课堂氛围轻松有趣，赵鸣华老师也凭借着自身过硬的专业素养积极调动同学们的积极性，点燃了同学的热情，师生们在共同合作学习的基础上，层层递进、积极思考、合作探究，造就了一个和谐、优秀的课堂，这样的课堂也荣获校方的肯定，在此次教学竞赛决赛中获得了一等奖的好成绩。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><br/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(71, 71, 71); letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; caret-color: red; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240509/1715242153491043740.png" title="1715242153491043740.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-09 155948.png" width="872" height="286" style="width: 872px; height: 286px;"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(71, 71, 71); letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; caret-color: red; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240509/1715242169215062245.png" title="1715242169215062245.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-09 155956.png" width="870" height="310" style="width: 870px; height: 310px;"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(71, 71, 71); letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; caret-color: red; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240509/1715242186502006896.png" title="1715242186502006896.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-09 160002.png" width="870" height="268" style="width: 870px; height: 268px;"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 30.9999px; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">（课堂互动中）</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">课虽尽而意无穷，赛虽止而思未尽。耕耘结硕果，奋戟再扬帆，荣誉是对过往努力的肯定，更是对未来发展的鼓舞。此次大赛充分展示了经济管理学院老师扎根课堂教书育人第一阵地，积极开展教育教学研究匠心育人精神。下一步，学院将发挥获奖教师的示范引领作用，持续推动教育教学创新，推进教育教学高质量发展。</span></p>